.TH AUXSAVER 1 "June 2026" "A/UX Workstation" "Local Commands"
.SH NAME
auxsaver \- bouncing-logo screensaver for the A/UX desktop
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B auxsaver
.SH DESCRIPTION
A DVD-style bouncing A/UX logo for the X session, built against the
local X11R6 client libraries.  Corner hits are celebrated quietly.
.SH SEE ALSO
bgroot(1), aux(7)
